channel.title: SpawnWork
channel.description:
Good day.
Seen as though a spawn server didn't really work out - This new server named spawnWork goes by its name, you need to earn everything. Even the server admins do and have. We will work on the new whitelist built into 1.3 BETA
So, you need 1.3 BETA files. As usual you say you want to join, you say if you've been convicted of anything on the official moparscape server and me and Si force decide if you're fit to be allowed in. Please don't expect an instant PM because it won't happen. For all those who really care it's hosted on Linux.
[b]Member List [/b]
[ul][li]Tomscape BETA[/li][li]Si force[/li][li]I Vain I[/li][li]Reyx7[/li][li]Krackkid[/li][li]Rix_[/li][li][s]RuneSpace[/s][/li][li]ranger squad[/li][li]Cane[/li][li]xx matty xx[/li][li]Newty[/li][li]TabbyKiller[/li][li]Burkey[/li][li]Noobs are ftw[/li][li]LilXCj[/li][li]Stupit[/li][li]asyo4[/li][/ul]
[b]IRC[/b]
Myself and Si force use the official minecraft IRC channel to talk to one another, so if you'd like to contact either of us then that's the way to go.
http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,476984.0.html
[b]Rules[/b]
1) No griefing 2) If people don't want you in their house, then you have to leave - if you refuse they can use force. 3) No stealing 4) All buildings must be legit 5) No cheating in any form
[size=14pt]UP[/size]
